{"tid":1268707,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紐約時報：香港警方是否對抗議者濫用武力？","createTime":"2019-06-30T10:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T11:19:14.000Z","uid":41404,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f5d66606b775578ea82e45867198a293bcba50ba","tid":1268707,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:57:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/zh-hant/2019/06/30/world/asia/did-hong-kong-police-abuse-protesters-what-videos-show.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Fzh-hant%2F2019%2F06%2F30%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fdid-hong-kong-police-abuse-protesters-what-videos-show.html&d=ZcVshzlQZ77dxUPC5JM1BPdnC8dk%2FAL47v0imjzWEG4%3D&h=4983ef27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/zh-hant/2019/06/30/world/asia/did-hong-kong-police-abuse-protesters-what-videos-show.html</a><br />\n使用催淚瓦斯、防暴彈，毆打和粗暴拖拉抗議者。人群控制方面的專家表示，香港警方在6月的一次示威活動中對抗議者過度使用武力。"},{"pid":"7ab994acf58f6638f05f6923e551b89f9d0d45ac","tid":1268707,"uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:57:56.000Z","msg":"香港有數十人表示，他們在6月的一次大規模示威中受到警方的傷害，示威活動反對的是一項具有爭議的法案，它將允許把逃犯引渡到中國大陸。<br />\n<br />\n為了評估香港警方是否存在過度使用武力的行為，《紐約時報》查閱了數以百計由目擊者發到網上的影片與照片，以及提交給我們WhatsApp爆料熱線的材料。人權團體國際特赦組織(Amnesty International)幫助檢視了這些影像。我們與人群控制方面的專家進行了交談 ，還採訪了20多名抗議者。<br />\n<br />\n影片顯示，在6月12日香港政府總部附近的大規模衝突中，抗議人群遭到警方毆打、用防暴彈射擊、在地上拖，並且被催淚瓦斯襲擊。他們受的傷包括肋骨淤青、手指骨折以及呼吸方面的問題。<br />\n<br />\n在一小群抗議人士向警方拋擲磚塊、瓶子及雨傘，並且試圖穿過全副武裝的警察布下的陣勢後，當局開始使用武力。<br />\n<br />\n但抗議活動大體上是和平的，人權團體譴責警方行為過度並且非法。1997年將其交還給中國大陸之前一直統治香港的英國政府，已經要求展開調查。香港官員表示，警方的行動是克制的。<br />\n<br />\n以下是證據顯示出來的情況。"},{"pid":"250617b5e0647d3546cfcb3da7f418a82f6140c4","tid":1268707,"uid":41404,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:58:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">針對手無寸鐵抗議人士的暴力</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n在一些例子裡，警方毆打了那些沒有構成明顯威脅的抗議者。<br />\n<br />\n57歲的吳應武是一名已退休的機械師，下面的影片顯示他走在政府辦公室外距離警戒線12碼內的地方。他讓警方不要再刺激抗議人士。然後開始大爆粗口。<br />\n<br />\n一名警察用槍瞄準了吳應武的方向，武器專家說，這把槍很可能裝有含胡椒噴霧的彈丸。一聲槍響過後，吳應武倒在地上，手捂下腹部。三名警察把他抓起帶離現場。"},{"pid":"92ed3c4c0b33a788101219e0622e85ad805a7d2b","tid":1268707,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T11:00:32.000Z","msg":"推爆死黑警<br />\n祝各黑警早日見老毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea02c2890f86f5934cc1149c4d01b9aba50d995","tid":1268707,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T11:01:15.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"7275cf8f215a2e5dea90f54fb595230a656f52c2","tid":1268707,"uid":43657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T11:05:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a769cb3ba8653bfaeb02bbd79b0f188ad1089454","tid":1268707,"uid":265197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T11:06:54.000Z","msg":"將今日撐警土共嘅暴力場面同警察嘅部署send番比佢地做對比睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5913f7042f15fd1aa0078c8ff8009531aba79956","tid":1268707,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T11:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3bf4ee2f0ca97377c17bee10f34c8a8b61bb7a","tid":1268707,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T11:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3424bbf01c19a64a12125af07bc4e530648d821c","tid":1268707,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T11:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/no